    <string name="weather_aqi_description_1">Air quality is satisfactory, and air pollution poses little or no risk.</string>
    <string name="weather_aqi_description_2">Air quality is acceptable.  However, there may be a risk for some people, particularly those who are unusually sensitive to air pollution.</string>
    <string name="weather_aqi_description_3">Members of sensitive groups may experience health effects.  The general public is less likely to be affected.</string>
    <string name="weather_aqi_description_4">Some members of the general public may experience health effects; members of sensitive groups may experience more serious health effects.</string>
    <string name="weather_aqi_description_5">Health alert!  The risk of health effects is increased for everyone.</string>
    <string name="weather_aqi_description_6">Health warning of emergency conditions!  Everyone is more likely to be affected.</string>
